  <brief_title>Randomized Trial of Intranasal Versus Intravenous Naloxone in Level of Consciousness in Suspected Opioid Overdose</brief_title>
  <official_title>Study of Routs of Naloxone Administration for Opioid Overdosed Patients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
